# Project: SkillShaper Pro V5

## Overview

SkillShaper Pro is a high-end, minimalist React-based visualization tool for "Talent Architecture" models (T-shape, M-shape, Pi-shape, V-shape). It's designed for tech founders and CEOs to visualize skill depth and breadth in the AI era.

## Tech Stack

- Framework: React (using Vite)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- Icons: Lucide React
- Persistence: LocalStorage

## Design Tokens (ps.one Brand)

- Background (Dark Blue): #000022
- Primary CTA (Pink): #FF00AA
- Accent (Bright Blue): #0000FF
- Elements: White / Transparent White

## Core Features

1. Interactive Columns: Drag-to-resize skill depth (5-100%).
2. Visual Style: "Plastic" look with gradients, inner gloss, and glows.
3. Presets: Buttons to transform layout (T, Pi, M, V shapes).
4. Bulk Editor: Modal to define skills line-by-line.
5. Profiles: Save/Load functionality using browser LocalStorage.

## AI Instructions

- Maintain the minimalist dark aesthetic.
- Ensure touch support for mobile devices.
- Focus on clean, modular React code within App (App.tsx in this repo).
